Guacamole
You can make this avocado salad smooth or chunky depending on your Servings: 4
tastes.
Ingredients
3 avocados - peeled, pitted, and mashed
1lime, juiced 1 teaspoon salt Y2 cup diced onion
3 tablespoons chopped fresh cilantro
2 roma (plum) tomatoes, diced
1 teaspoon minced garlic
1 pinch ground cayenne pepper (Optional)
Prep: 10 mins Total: 10 mins

Yield: 4 servings
Directions
Step 1
In a medium bowl, mash together the avocados, lime juice, and salt. Mixin onion, cilantro, tomatoes, and garlic. Stir in cayenne pepper. Refrigerate 1 hour for best flavor, or serve immediately.
